# Vanilla Train Stop for Fuel

* Does not use LTN (or any other mod).
* Designed for 2 header trains.
* Train station is placed 1 tile ahead of existing trains
* 1-1 Fuel train must be provided
* Automatically disables station unless it needs fuel (station reads chest contents)
* Fuel inserters are disabled when fuel train is present by reading train contents. 
 * Enabled when Solid Fuel = 0 (i.e. train does not contain Solid fuel)
 * This means the inserters are disabled when train *does* contain Solid Fuel
 * Enabled at all other times
* Currently setup for solid fuel. (Signal must be changed for different fuel types)
* Combinator is needed to turn chest contents signal into **F**. This prevents the station from loading fuel back into the fuel car
